SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you had a sensation of not emptying your bladder completely after you finished urinating?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Sensation of Not Emptying Bladder

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you had to urinate again less than 2 hours after you finished urinating?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Urinate Again Less Than 2 Hours

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you found you stopped and started again several times when you urinated?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Stop Start Several Times Urinated

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you found it difficult to postpone urination?
International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you had a weak urinary stream?

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IPS01-Push or Strain to Begin Urination
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month or so, how often have you had to push or strain to begin urination?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Push or Strain to Begin Urination

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IPS01-Times Get Up to Urinate at Night
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - During the last month, how many times did you most typically get up to urinate from the time you went to bed at night until the time you got up in the morning?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Times Get Up to Urinate at Night

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - AUA symptom total score.

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IPS01-Life With Symptoms Feel About It
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Prostate Symptom Score - If you were to spend the rest of your life with your prostate symptoms just as they are now, how would you feel about that?
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: IPSS - Life With Symptoms Feel About It
